HEADWORD: Pantisocracy
<hw>Pan`ti*soc"ra*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Panto-</ets> + Gr. <?/ equal + <?/ to rule.]</ety> <def>A
